{"tid":97253,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】疑似鏗哥未來流出!!!","createTime":"2017-01-27T13:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T03:11:36.000Z","uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cad22d7d2e62484c5cae8e8c3bc913e3b95e122b","tid":97253,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"涉收黑幫賄免費嫖妓 被捕O記高級督察為港大尖子<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170126/56226676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170126%2F56226676&d=OQn54MhRhb3uFRN17xZq%2FmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7d74f4ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170126%2F56226676&h=3c68d120\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170126/56226676</a><br />\n<br />\n廉署日前拘捕港島總區刑事總部警司吳偉漢、O記高級督察陳嘉健和港島總區反黑組探員鍾文浩，當中有人涉嫌收受黑幫賄款及獲免費嫖妓，作為協助申請酒牌、查閱警方機密資料、包庇及通風報訊的報酬。翻查資料，涉案被捕的陳嘉健，2010年在<span style=\"color: red;\">港大工程系畢業</span>，昔日有報道形容他是「尖子」。陳受訪時曾稱破案是其工作最大的滿足感，「拘捕疑犯，繩之於法，推動我無懼挑戰，不斷向前。」"},{"pid":"0ef860c7baf14893d10d6a2aec85eb246ddfa3d3","tid":97253,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0ac97ee236f7ba53bf1c8ef3a5dcd0ff9effa8","tid":97253,"uid":15883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"鏗哥畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b69b098befa6fb00032c979b80b04a5fe44c2c","tid":97253,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鏗哥畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該final year 如果當年佢有transfer credit<br />\n但應該pre-final year 因為exchange? 好似係"},{"pid":"bdb29451d9fd42d752a6916